"{\"uid\": \"lakeplacidnews.com-news-local-news-2024-03-21-olympic-motor-inn-changes-name-not-spirit\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Mar 21, 2024  The Devlin hotel, Main Street, Lake Placid (News photo - Sydney Emerson)  LAKE PLACID - The Devlin hotel changed hands in 2022, but did not let go of its legacy as a Lake Placid staple.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4100029960644574e-16, \"text\": \"Lake Placid\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 71, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999925645005481, \"rank\": 3.7831072296996053e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerson_Electric\", \"score\": 0.9370073904673853, \"rank\": 0.06711758167060347, \"text\": \"Emerson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerson_Electric\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerson_Electric\"}, {\"begin\": 88, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4100029960644574e-16, \"text\": \"LAKE PLACID\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the name has changed, the new owners are working to renovate the almost 70-year-old hotel while maintaining its spirit.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are trying not to brand it but let each individual hotel keep its local feel,\\\"said Andrew Milne, owner of several Tri-Lakes hotels.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999707096807535, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Milne\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tri-Lakes,_Indiana\", \"score\": 0.6044949122402518, \"rank\": 0.4285714285714115, \"text\": \"Tri-Lakes\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tri-Lakes,_Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tri-Lakes,_Indiana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Milne said he does not technically own the Devlin.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Formerly Art Devlin's Olympic Motor Inn, the hotel is now run by BNB-Buddy, a local hotel management company.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company owns and operates Sara Placid Inn & Suites and The Ashley in Saranac Lake, the latter named for Andrew's wife Ashley, who owns BNB-Buddy.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"score\": 0.9566613205072132, \"rank\": 0.03481225279151521, \"text\": \"Ashley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Art Devlin, Lake Placid's current mayor, sold the hotel for $4.4 million in 2022.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.8717465996187553, \"rank\": 0.14705882352940106, \"text\": \"Art Devlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\"}, {\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4100029960644574e-16, \"text\": \"Lake Placid\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Winter_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He bought the hotel from his father - Art Devlin - in 1992 after growing up there as his father had.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After decades of being on call 24/7, Devlin said he was ready to pass it on.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was just time to get out,\\\"he said.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BNB-Buddy's goal for The Devlin is to modernize it, but not to redo it.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly, Milne said, changes will be limited to room renovations and a\\\"nice, new sign.\\\"\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Changing the name of the hotel was due to several factors, but dropping the\\\"motor-inn\\\"part was intentional, Milne said.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than the older motor-inn style, Milne said it will have a more\\\"boutique\\\"feel.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other part of the name, the\\\"Olympic,\\\"can not be used anymore.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hotel's first name was\\\"Devlin's Motel\\\"when it opened in 1953.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, the mayor's father was considered an\\\"amateur\\\"athlete, not yet allowed to monetize the Olympic name, despite competing as a ski jumper in the 1952 Olympic Winter Games in Oslo, Norway.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1757, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo_bid_for_the_2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9923567683173773, \"rank\": 0.007702100621913705, \"text\": \"Oslo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo_bid_for_the_2018_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo_bid_for_the_2018_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9998480401296899, \"rank\": 0.00015193892674621764, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Devlin went on to compete in the same event during the 1956 Games in Cortina d'Ampezzo, Italy.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}, {\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cortina d'Ampezzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cortina d'Ampezzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999747586523603, \"rank\": 1.4011142769141236e-05, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He changed the name to Art Devlin's Olympic Motor Inn after retiring from competition in 1960.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1889, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.8717465996187553, \"rank\": 0.14705882352940106, \"text\": \"Art Devlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_Devlin_(baseball)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now,\\\"Olympic\\\"is trademarked.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The motor-inn was grandfathered in since it started using the name prior, but that is not the case for the new owners, Milne said.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, BNB-Buddy is awaiting approval from Olympic authorities to use\\\"Olympic\\\"in the hotel's tag proposed tagline,\\\"An Olympic Inn at the heart of Lake Placid.\\\"\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RAY BROOK - The legal battle over a proposed howitzer artillery cannon t